<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have been hunting for unshattered caster beads for over a week and for many hours a day.  I am seriously doubting anything could be worth all this frustration.  On the good side I made two levels killing off the goblins and turning in the shattered beads and necklaces.  If anyone has anyhints I would love to hear them cause I am about to give up on finding them.  Thanks    -Fuzznutkins bearer of free torches<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
