<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The Goblin caster that drops the lore item concerned seems to only spawn inside one of the igloos is the Soutern most gob camp. I was after necklaces for a war quest and then the caster pops and drops this. hehe.<BR>
<BR>
Warning. The caster hits hard if you are under level 9ish, he is a rare spawn and the Lore item is  a rare drop. So be patient. Spawn time at this camp is about 5min.</font></td></tr></table>
